dct_title_s: Wisconsin Wetland Inventory Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin 1994
dct_description_sm: This feature dataset set contains a polygon data layer that represents wetlands greater than 2 acres and a point data layer that represents wetlands smaller than 2 acres for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 1994. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, FondDuLacCounty_Wetlands_1994.gdb. The dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources in 2006.[Wetlands for Fond du Lac County, WI. The data layer is in Wisconsin Transverse Mercator (WTM) projection system, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustments.][The wetland layer includes a series of polygon coverages/shapefiles and point coverages/shapefiles that are digitized from 1:24,000 scale Wisconsin Wetland Inventory (WWI) maps. The point coverage includes information for wetlands smaller than 2 or 5 acres (depending on year), dammed ponds and excavated ponds. Map tiles for both sets of data correspond to Public Land Survey System (PLSS) Townships.]
